beasnstalk is aplatform as a service 
that makes it easy to deploy, manage & scale web application& service on aws


EXAMPLE:- 
    a developer upload a java web application to elastic beanstalk , aws automatically creates ec2 instance , load balancer & auto scaling configruation


USES OF BEANSTALK:-

      1) easy application deployment:-
                    upload your code & deploy application quickly

      2) auto scaling:-
                    automatically scales resources based on the traffic

     3) load baalncing:-

     4) monitoring:-
                   integrates with cloudwatch for monitoring application health

     5)infrastructure managment:-
                    automatically handle ec2 instance , load balancer & scaling

     6)support language:-
                    java , python , php , nodes , net , go , docker
